'''裕廊坊'''（{{lang-en|Jurong Point}}）是位于[[新加坡|新加坡]]西部{{tsl|en|Jurong West||裕廊西}}新镇的[[购物中心|购物中心]]。

==历史==
1995年12月裕廊坊购物中心开幕。1996年3月，新加坡第一家设置在商场内的公共图书馆{{tsl|en|Jurong West Public Library||裕廊西公共图书馆}}正式于裕廊坊购物中心开幕。<ref name="Ho 2018">{{cite web | last=Ho | first=Olivia | title=Book depositories: NLB makes concerted effort to spruce up libraries | website=The Straits Times | date=2018-02-11 | url=https://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/arts/book-depositories | access-date=2018-08-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180213004426/http://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/arts/book-depositories | archive-date=2018-02-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年裕廊坊购物中心正式完成扩建，成为当时新加坡郊区最大的购物中心之一。<ref name="Sue-Ann 2017">{{cite web | last=Sue-Ann | first=Cheow | title=Revamped FairPrice outlet at Jurong Point reopens | website=The Straits Times | date=2017-12-07 | url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/newly-revamped-ntuc-fairprice-outlet-at-jurong-point-reopens | access-date=2018-08-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180116175704/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/newly-revamped-ntuc-fairprice-outlet-at-jurong-point-reopens | archive-date=2018-01-16 | dead-url=no }}</ref>同时，裕廊坊购物中心楼上的私人公寓项目“The Centris”也正式落成。2009年1月28日[[文礼巴士转换站|文礼巴士转换站]]也搬迁至落裕廊坊购物中心内，并且成为新加坡第4个综合交通枢纽，与附近的[[文禮地鐵站|文禮地鐵站]]链接在一起。文礼巴士转换站也是新加坡最多巴士路线停靠的巴士转换站。<ref name="Chan 2009">{{cite web | last=Chan | first=Rachel | title=Biggest air-con interchange opens | website=AsiaOne, Asia's Leading News Portal, Get Latest News at AsiaOne | date=2009-12-28 | url=http://news.asiaone.com/News/AsiaOne%2BNews/Singapore/Story/A1Story20091228-188336.html | access-date=2018-08-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402051723/http://news.asiaone.com/News/AsiaOne%2BNews/Singapore/Story/A1Story20091228-188336.html | archive-date=2017-04-02 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2016年10月，裕廊坊购物中心的开发商Guthrie GTS以及Lee Kim Tah Holdings正式摘牌。过后开发商以20亿新加坡元的价钱出售廊坊购物中心。<ref name="AsiaOne 2016"/> {{tsl|en|National Trade Union Congress||新加坡职中联合会}}的子公司Mercatus Co-operative Limited最终以22亿新元的价钱收购了购物中心。<ref name="Meixian 2017">{{cite web | last=Meixian | first=Lee | title=SPH Reit looking to acquisitions overseas | website=The Straits Times | date=2017-12-01 | url=https://www.straitstimes.com/business/sph-reit-looking-to-acquisitions-overseas | access-date=2018-08-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214063649/http://www.straitstimes.com/business/sph-reit-looking-to-acquisitions-overseas | archive-date=2018-02-14 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

